{"tid":1911824,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街了買咗四月泰國機票。。。。。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-03-05T15:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T22:20:36.000Z","uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"c476b03a8521242b83643e1a0d5e2992432ea300","tid":1911824,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"😭"},{"pid":"6c5334a88895f22fc2d07cd077a436eda5195916","tid":1911824,"uid":158899,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"14日入住幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6039b021b23f02d286bad9b2275b1622435f2dc5","tid":1911824,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />泰國將香港在內的11個國家及地區列為武漢肺炎高危地區，呼籲入境國民需自我隔離14日。 榜上有名的國家及地區包括日本、德國、南韓、中國、台灣、法國、新加坡、意大利、伊朗、香港、澳門。 來自以上11地的泰國公民，需要自隔離14日，除非得到衛生官員的許可。在泰國沒有永久住所人士，必須在抵達時向官員出示證據，證明官員在14天之內可在哪裡找到他們。 泰國副總理兼衞生部長阿努廷亦一度在社交網發文，指以上11地的入境旅客需自我隔離14日，但之後刪除貼文。香港旅議會總幹事陳張樂怡亦澄清，有關規定只適用於泰國人，不影響香港旅客。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-03-2020/60562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-03-2020%2F60562&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=d514b576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-03-2020/60562</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2020"},{"pid":"7dfc0e9cacbdc94cee25f88b4ca1ff871317aa9a","tid":1911824,"uid":71166,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"6c5334a88895f22fc2d07cd077a436eda5195916","tid":1911824,"uid":158899,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"14日入住幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2